## Make the coolest dance and win concert tickets, or even meet Band!

In every city on the <a href="https://www.coldplay.com/tour/">tour</a> we will pick two students and two chaperones to receive free tickets to the concert — we will pick from projects posted or submitted by individual/single students. We will also select at least one lucky classroom globally to have a video call with the band, and we will pick among the projects that feature entire classrooms dancing.

